This topic contains the release notes for VMware Spring Cloud® Data Flow for Kubernetes version 1.3.

## <a id="1-3-0"></a>v1.3.0

**Release Date: June 14, 2021**

### <a id='features'></a> Features

Features included in this release:

- Spring Cloud Data Flow has been updated to SCDF Pro version 1.3.0
- Spring Cloud Skipper has been updated to 2.7.0
- Composed Task Runner 2.8.0 container image is now provided
